= Template Sample =

Templates are a tool for adding boilerplate text and meta data to new items.
They are useful when a wiki will have many pages with a similar format.

Under MoinMoin 2, any item having the tag 'template' is a template.
Under MoinMoin 1.9.x, any page ending in 'Template' was a template.

Templates are specific to a content type and namespace.
This template can only be used to create new 'text/x.moin.wiki' items in namespace help-en.
To use a template, create a new moin wiki item and choose the link with a template's name rather than the 'create this item from scratch' link.

Please be aware that the ACL, the summary and the tags are also copied from the template.

